assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Futaba Industrial Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells automobile parts, information environment equipment, equipment for external sales, and agricultural equipment in Japan and internationally. The company offers exhaust system parts comprising exhaust systems and exhaust manifolds; environment system parts, such as exhaust heat recovery and diesel exhaust gas post-treatment devices; body parts and interior parts, including body frame parts and instrument panel reinforcements; suspension parts comprising front suspension sub-frames, trailing arms, rear axle beams, and engine undercovers; and fuel system parts, such as fuel inlet pipes and canisters. It also provides office equipment parts comprising sheet feeders, tray modules, and squarefold trimmers, as well as multifunction copiers. The company was incorporated in 1935 and is headquartered in Okazaki, Japan.
